	"system": {
		"description": "<p>At 8th level, your authority over fire deepens. You gain the following feature:</p><ul><li><p>You are immune to fire damage.</p></li><li><p>You ignore any resistances a creature may have with fire damage and creatures immune to fire damage are only resistant to your fire damage.</p></li><li><p>You can sense open flames within 1 mile. You instinctively know the direction and approximate size of any flame that lasts longer than a round or that was started by magic.</p></li><li><p>You gain one inexperienced follower or your inexperienced follower becomes seasoned.</p></li></ul>",
